<p>Price Trackers allows users to search and set price notifications for Amazon products.
  The app is catered to users who hold off on buying products in hopes of a price decrease.
  Users can set a price alert on any product for one to five days.
  If the price of their selected product drops, they will be notified via text with a link to the product.
  Users are able to add multiple alerts, manage current alerts, and see their recently viewed products. </p>


